	        <div class="intro">
	            <p>These templates take the victoria.ac.nz patterns and combine them to meet common user needs. We use them to maintain a consistent design across our services.</p>
	        </div>
	        <p>Design for small screens first using a single column layout. Use white space to create a visual hierarchy on the page.</p>
	        <p>The default maximum page width is 70em, but hub pages can go wider if the content requires it.</p>
	        <p>Optimise for different screen sizes, but don’t make assumptions about what devices people are using.</p>
